// sanitizeXML strips any DOCTYPE declarations (and thus all entity definitions,
// including external entities, parameter entities, and entity references that
// could trigger XXE or SSRF). Go's encoding/xml does not resolve external
// entities by default, but it *does* process internal entity declarations in
